{"subject_key": "data_structure", "subject_name": "数据结构", "year": 2022, "docx_mtime": 1781481024.0, "questions": [{"id": "data_structure_2022_1", "year": 2022, "number": 1, "type": "选择题", "content": "第 1 题", "image_urls": ["/static/exam_papers/11408/data_structure/2022/img_0.jpg"], "options": {"A": "O(log n)", "B": "B. O(n)", "C": "C. O(nlogn)", "D": "D. O(n²)"}, "answer": "B", "stem": "第 1 题", "ocr_quality": "medium", "need_manual_check": true}, {"id": "data_structure_2022_2", "year": 2022, "number": 2, "type": "选择题", "content": "第 2 题", "image_urls": ["/static/exam_papers/11408/data_structure/2022/img_1.jpg"], "options": {"A": "若 in 是 ST 的入栈序列，则不能判断 out 是否为其可能的出栈序列", "B": "若 out 是 ST 的出栈序列，则不能判断 in 是否为其可能的入栈序列", "C": "若 in 是 ST 的入栈序列，out 是对应 in 的出栈序列，则 in 与 out 一定不同", "D": "若 in 是 ST 的入栈序列，out 是对应 in 的出栈序列，则 in 与 out 可能互为倒序"}, "answer": "D", "stem": "2.有限符号集S,in,out均为S中所有元素的任意排列。对于初始为空的栈ST，下列叙述正确的是（）", "ocr_quality": "high", "need_manual_check": false}, {"id": "data_structure_2022_3", "year": 2022, "number": 3, "type": "选择题", "content": "第 3 题", "image_urls": ["/static/exam_papers/11408/data_structure/2022/img_2.jpg"], "options": {"A": "仅I", "B": "仅III", "C": "仅Ⅱ、Ⅲ", "D": "仅Ⅱ、IV"}, "answer": "B", "stem": "3.若结点p与q在二叉树T中的中序遍历序列中相邻，且p在q之前，则下列p与q的关系中，不可能是()", "ocr_quality": "high", "need_manual_check": false}, {"id": "data_structure_2022_4", "year": 2022, "number": 4, "type": "选择题", "content": "第 4 题", "image_urls": ["/static/exam_papers/11408/data_structure/2022/img_3.jpg"], "options": {}, "answer": "C", "stem": "4.若三叉树T中有244个结点(叶结点高度为1)，则T的高度至少是()", "ocr_quality": "medium", "need_manual_check": true}, {"id": "data_structure_2022_5", "year": 2022, "number": 5, "type": "选择题", "content": "第 5 题", "image_urls": ["/static/exam_papers/11408/data_structure/2022/img_4.jpg"], "options": {"A": "A. T1 与 T2 的结点数相同", "B": "B. T1 的高度大于 T2 的高度", "C": "C. 出现频次不同的字符在 T1 中处于不同层", "D": "D. 出现频次不同的字符在 T2 中处于相同的层"}, "answer": "D", "stem": "5.对任意给定的含n(n>2)个字符的有限集S，用二叉树表示S的哈夫曼编码集和定长编码集，分别得到二叉树T1,T2。下列叙述中，正确的是（）", "ocr_quality": "high", "need_manual_check": false}, {"id": "data_structure_2022_6", "year": 2022, "number": 6, "type": "选择题", "content": "第 6 题", "image_urls": ["/static/exam_papers/11408/data_structure/2022/img_5.jpg"], "options": {"A": "当|V|>E时，G一定是连通的", "B": "当|V|<E时，G一定是连通的", "C": "当|V|=E-1时，G一定是不连通的", "D": "当|V|>E+1时，G一定是不连通的"}, "answer": "D", "stem": "6.对于无向图 G=<V,E>，下列选项中，正确的是（）", "ocr_quality": "high", "need_manual_check": false}, {"id": "data_structure_2022_7", "year": 2022, "number": 7, "type": "选择题", "content": "第 7 题", "image_urls": ["/static/exam_papers/11408/data_structure/2022/img_6.jpg"], "options": {"A": "A.e", "B": "B.g", "C": "C.h", "D": "D.j"}, "answer": "B", "stem": "7.下图是一个有 10 个活动的AOE网，时间余量最大的活动是（）", "ocr_quality": "high", "need_manual_check": false}, {"id": "data_structure_2022_8", "year": 2022, "number": 8, "type": "选择题", "content": "第 8 题", "image_urls": ["/static/exam_papers/11408/data_structure/2022/img_7.jpg"], "options": {"A": "A.60，90，280", "B": "B.60，90，350", "C": "C.60，85，110，350", "D": "D.60，90，110，350"}, "answer": "D", "stem": "第 8 题", "ocr_quality": "medium", "need_manual_check": true}, {"id": "data_structure_2022_9", "year": 2022, "number": 9, "type": "选择题", "content": "第 9 题", "image_urls": ["/static/exam_papers/11408/data_structure/2022/img_8.jpg"], "options": {"A": "仅 I、II", "B": "仅 I、III", "C": "仅 II、III", "D": "I、II、III"}, "answer": "D", "stem": "第 9 题", "ocr_quality": "medium", "need_manual_check": true}, {"id": "data_structure_2022_10", "year": 2022, "number": 10, "type": "选择题", "content": "第 10 题", "image_urls": ["/static/exam_papers/11408/data_structure/2022/img_9.jpg"], "options": {"A": "将两个有序表合并为一个新的有序表", "B": "将 M 划分为两部分，两部分的元素个数大致相等", "C": "将 M 划分为 n 个部分，每个部分中仅含所有一个元素", "D": "将 M 划分为两部分，一部分元素的值均小于另一部分元素的值"}, "answer": "A", "stem": "使用二路归并排序对含 n 个元素的数组 M 进行排序时,对二路归并操作的功能是()", "ocr_quality": "high", "need_manual_check": false}, {"id": "data_structure_2022_11", "year": 2022, "number": 11, "typ